extends ../layout

block content 
  
    .container.col-lg-10.col-10.text-center
        h1.fw-light.text-center.text-lg.mt-5(style='') Our Recent Tour Destinations 
            span.material-symbols-outlined(style='color: green; font-size: 35px')  push_pin
        hr    
        p Coming to Pakistan having lots of tourism plans in your mind? Then let us be the reliable companion of your journey. We provide affordable Pakistan tour packages across the country. Either youâ€™re inspired from north Pakistan or even have a dream of historical site's excursion, we're offering comfortable travel and luxurious stay services to visit the best tourist places of Pakistan. 
